---
title: Korean-Style Tofu & Garlic Rice with Sesame Veggies & Plant-Based Mayo
description: If you’re familiar with bibimbap, the Korean ‘mixed rice’ dish, then you’ll love this HelloFresh plant-based version. So, divvy
up the fragrant rice, pile on the tofu and toppings, then mix it all together for a glorious fusion of flavours and textures.

*Due to local availability, we’ve replaced some of your ingredients. They may be a little different to what’s pictured, but just as delicious!*
